*mantisbt-1.0.8-r1 (30 Dec 2007)

  30 Dec 2007; <pva@gentoo.org>
  +files/mantisbt-1.0.8-avoid-XSS-in-file_api.php.patch,
  +mantisbt-1.0.8-r1.ebuild:
  Fixes "Upload File" Script Insertion Vulnerability, bug 203791, reported by
  Pierre-Yves Rofes <py AT gentoo.org>.

  10 Dec 2007; <pva@gentoo.org> mantisbt-1.0.8.ebuild:
  Fixed apache2 DEPEND, bug #201822. Thank Nick Devito <nick AT nick125.com>
  for report and Gunnar Wrobel <wrobel AT gentoo.org> for the fix.

  18 Nov 2007; <pva@gentoo.org> mantisbt-1.0.8.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, see Kingtaco's letter on -core at Tue, 13 Nov 2007

  05 Nov 2007; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org>
  mantisbt-1.0.8.ebuild:
  stable x86, bug 197988

  04 Nov 2007; Lars Weiler <pylon@gentoo.org> mantisbt-1.0.8.ebuild:
  stable ppc, bug #197988

  03 Nov 2007; <pva@gentoo.org> -mantisbt-1.0.7.ebuild,
  mantisbt-1.0.8.ebuild:
  Remove old. Quotation fixes.

